    I don't like the ofed name because isn't "ofed" the name of the
    standards body and not the protocol being used?&nbsp; I'd be in favor of
    renaming the btl ibverbs after the library the btl accesses.&nbsp;
    However isn't this btl (and the underlying library) used with
    networks other than IB?<br>
